{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"链接类型：preload","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Link_types/preload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>关键字 <strong><code>preload</code></strong> 作为元素&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a> 的属性&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link#attr-rel\"><code>rel</code></a> 的值，表示用户十分有可能需要在当前浏览中加载目标资源，所以浏览器必须预先获取和缓存对应资源。&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>更多细节见<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Link_types/preload\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通过 rel=\"preload\"进行内容预加载 (en-US)</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#link-type-preload\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">preload</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.link.rel.preload","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Link_types/preload/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"规范","id":"specifications"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"关键字 preload 作为元素 <link> 的属性 rel 的值，表示用户十分有可能需要在当前浏览中加载目标资源，所以浏览器必须预先获取和缓存对应资源。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Link types: preload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Types de liens : preload","locale":"fr","na